# 4. Technology Selection and Justification

The selected technologies were chosen based on performance, integration capabilities, scalability, and cost.

| Technology          | Purpose                | Justification                                    |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| Python              | Programming Language   | Large AI ecosystem and rapid development         |
| FastAPI             | Backend Framework      | High performance and automatic API documentation |
| CrewAI              | Agent Framework        | Multi-agent workflow orchestration               |
| Groq                | Cloud LLM              | Fast inference and high-quality responses        |
| Ollama              | Local LLM              | Offline execution and API independence           |
| HTML/CSS/JavaScript | Frontend               | Lightweight and easy integration                 |
| JSON                | Prototype Data Storage | Simple and suitable for Proof of Concept         |

## Why CrewAI?

CrewAI enables role-based AI agents that independently solve specialized business tasks while collaborating through a centralized workflow.

Benefits include:

* Separation of responsibilities
* Better maintainability
* Easier scalability
* Improved code organization

## Why Groq?

Groq provides:

* Fast AI inference
* Cloud scalability
* Low latency
* High-quality language generation

## Why Ollama?

Ollama provides:

* Offline execution
* No API dependency
* Zero API cost
* Improved system reliability



