* Docker monitoring



# 10. Conclusion

The proposed AI Customer Support Automation System provides a practical and scalable solution for automating customer interactions using a modular multi-agent architecture.

The combination of FastAPI, CrewAI, Groq, and Ollama delivers a flexible hybrid AI platform capable of generating intelligent responses while maintaining high availability through automatic model fallback.

The architecture minimizes operational costs, simplifies maintenance, and enables future expansion through additional AI agents and enterprise-grade infrastructure components.

Based on the technical evaluation and prototype implementation, this architecture is recommended as a strong foundation for developing production-ready AI customer support solutions capable of serving growing business requirements efficiently and reliably.

